  "title": "Regional Sales Manager – Office & Printing Solutions",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Define and execute regional sales and go-to-market strategies.</li>\n  <li>Lead business growth in identified markets and drive pipeline development.</li>\n  <li>Oversee revenue and KPI performance across all country teams.</li>\n  <li>Implement standardized sales frameworks and CRM practices regionwide.</li>\n  <li>Mentor country leaders and develop next-generation talent.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate closely with internal business units to align solutions with client needs.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>10+ years in B2B hardware sales, including 5+ years of regional management.</li>\n  <li>Proven experience in corporate and government sales across Southeast Asia.</li>\n  <li>Strategic thinker with strong commercial acumen and cross-cultural leadership skills.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and stakeholder engagement abilities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
